      "rationale": "Validation metric E/uval computed per ASME V&V 40 Section 9 for stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm. All three QoIs satisfy E/uval <1.96. Percentage differences: stiffness 3.1%, yield force 4.2%, force at 40 mm 7.8%. Pre-specified acceptance bounds met. Gradation 3 achieved."
