      "rationale": "Assessment of QoI relevance to clinical performance endpoints was considered beyond the scope of this validation study. The team noted that stiffness and yield force are standard ASTM F1717 outputs but did not formally evaluate whether these surrogates adequately represent in vivo fatigue or subsidence risk. This factor was deferred as 'beyond scope' without a documented plan to address the gap, despite the modelRiskLevel of 3 requiring heightened scrutiny of all factors."
